[[_service]]
=== Service

The IIS has limited service relative to a standard department.
Over time, IIS service roles are likely to grow.

==== Social Media Coordinator ({social-media})

* Administer Facebook page
* Update Facebook page with IIS events and recognition

==== IIS Undergraduate Coordinator ({iis-undergraduate-coordinator})

* Advise students
* Maintain the degree website
* Update available courses each semester
* Monitor program outcomes with respect to goals

==== IIS Graduate Coordinator ({iis-graduate-coordinator})

* Advise students
* Admit students into program
* For non-degree students, clear to register for classes each semester
* Approve course substitutions
* Certify completion of requirements
* Monitor program outcomes with respect to goals
